graph TD
    A([Platform\nTelegram / User]) -->|raw message| B

    B[Channel Adapter\nConverts to unified Message format]

    B --> C{Has\nAttachments?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Inbound Processors]
    C -->|No| E

    D --> D1[file_persistence\nSave to uploads/YYYY-MM-DD/]
    D1 --> D2{Audio?}
    D2 -->|Yes| D3[whisper\nTranscribe to .txt sibling]
    D2 -->|No| D4{Document?}
    D3 --> D4
    D4 -->|Yes| D5[docling\nConvert to .md sibling]
    D4 -->|No| E
    D5 --> E

    E[Command Router\nCheck for slash command prefix]
    E --> F{Is Slash\nCommand?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Command Handler\n/new  /status  /model  /help ...]
    F -->|No| H

    G -->|direct reply| Z

    H[QueueManager\nAssign to lane, debounce, apply queue mode]

    H --> I{Queue\nMode?}
    I -->|collect| J1[Buffer message\nWait for debounce window]
    I -->|steer| J2[Pass through\nFlag pending for middleware]
    I -->|interrupt| J3[Signal interrupt\nAbort current run]
    I -->|followup| J4[Chain after\ncurrent run completes]

    J1 --> K
    J2 --> K
    J3 --> K
    J4 --> K

    K[MessageProcessor\nDequeue, build combined context]

    K --> L[AgentRunner\nInvoke LangGraph create_react_agent]

    L --> M[Middleware Stack]
    M --> M1[QueueAwareToolMiddleware\nCheck for pending messages per tool call]
    M1 --> M2[ApprovalToolMiddleware\nGate dangerous tools for human approval]
    M2 --> N

    N[Agent Processing\nLangGraph ReAct loop]
    N --> N1{Need\nTool?}
    N1 -->|Yes| N2[Tool Execution\nFilesystem, search, browser, spawn ...]
    N2 --> N3{Middleware\nSignal?}
    N3 -->|steer: redirect| K
    N3 -->|interrupt: abort| K
    N3 -->|approval needed| O[Approval Gate\nSend inline keyboard to user]
    O -->|approved| N2
    O -->|denied| N
    N3 -->|continue| N
    N1 -->|No| P[Generate Response]

    P --> Q[AgentRunner\nReturn final output]
    Q --> Z

    Z([Channel Adapter\nSend response to platform])

    style A fill:#2d6a9f,color:#fff
    style Z fill:#2d6a9f,color:#fff
    style G fill:#5a3e8a,color:#fff
    style O fill:#8a5a3e,color:#fff
    style D1 fill:#2e6b4f,color:#fff
    style D3 fill:#2e6b4f,color:#fff
    style D5 fill:#2e6b4f,color:#fff
    style N fill:#3e5a8a,color:#fff
    style N2 fill:#3e5a8a,color:#fff
